{"tid":1261329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国孔子頭觀音像曝光淪笑柄  當局慌忙偷拆又被發現","createTime":"2019-06-27T07:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T08:01:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"baff2a84eb2a85b3076cb6e7c06ed4c0a9c99ab6","tid":1261329,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZROIzs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZROIzs.png&h=877b5ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔子頭觀音像拆除前後對比。（合成照，擷取自《寒冬》）<br />\n<br />\n中國全面鎮壓宗教，拆像毀廟之舉時有所聞，為求自保，山東第一觀音像日前被信徒整容成「孔子」以避禍，不料消息曝光後慘淪笑柄。當局惱羞之下連忙在半個月內以「園內施工」為由企圖偷偷拆除，不意外地又被發現，欲蓋彌彰之意再惹譏嘲。<br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌刊文指出，在當前整肅宗教風聲鶴唳的氣氛下，山東省民眾為保住著名的「聖泉觀音像」，特地耗資百萬將其整容成「孔子」，該像才得以續命留存。然而，此一奇景經《寒冬》報導後引發海外輿論譁然，當地政府疑因面子掛不住，遂速令有關部門將其秘密拆除。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，上月初消息外傳後，當局在同月中旬火速出動大批人員，將園區重重封鎖，對外則以「園內施工、禁止入內」等理由驅離民眾。經過短短10幾天的工程，孔子頭顱被斫毀，觀音身也被徹底夷平，此一「奇觀」終告徹底消失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2835349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2835349&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0djbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=7152de38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2835349&h=6fee2434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2835349</a>"},{"pid":"cce45a77bf8bc01ef4c6f7b385febc16824f8e5f","tid":1261329,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"孔子頭觀音身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023f34f1588d22b5fd403c9d1deb06fc363fb111","tid":1261329,"uid":56323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cce45a77bf8bc01ef4c6f7b385febc16824f8e5f","tid":1261329,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":